-1724075559578-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="GameInfo_gameInfoTopSection__xKLGy"><div class="Breadcrumbs_breadcrumbs__L3mrb"><div><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/">Games</a><div class="Breadcrumbs_separator__yCVN1">Â»</div></div><div><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/c/io">.io</a><div class="Breadcrumbs_separator__yCVN1">Â»</div></div><div><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/c/adventure">Adventure</a><div class="Breadcrumbs_separator__yCVN1">Â»</div></div><div><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/minecraft">Minecraft</a></div><div class="Breadcrumbs_separator__yCVN1">Â»</div><div><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/game/bloxdhop-io">Bloxd.io</a></div></div><div class="GameInfo_containerWithPadding__z9aMp"><h1>Bloxd.io</h1></div><div class="GameInfo_gameUnderTitle__EyUXF"><button class="Button_czyButton__y8IRs Button_czyButton--contained--grey__sz05o Button_czyButton--height34__0zFYJ"><span role="img" aria-hidden="true" class="Icon_icon__OracF Icon_icon-share__KNo_C Icon_size20__yF8AY"></span><span>Share</span></button></div><dl class="GameSummary_gameSummaryTable__KxE9A"><dt class="GameSummary_gameTableRowHeader__qmvU_">Developer</dt><dd class="GameSummary_gameTableRowContent__RW5fE"><div><div class="GameInfo_styledDevName__MnwFN">Arthur</div></div></dd><dt class="GameSummary_gameTableRowHeader__qmvU_">Rating</dt><dd class="GameSummary_gameTableRowContent__RW5fE"><div style="font-weight:900">8.6</div><div style="font-weight:400;font-size:12px;margin-left:4px">(<!-- -->1,288,431 votes<!-- -->)</div></dd><dt class="GameSummary_gameTableRowHeader__qmvU_">Released</dt><dd class="GameSummary_gameTableRowContent__RW5fE">March 2021</dd><dt class="GameSummary_gameTableRowHeader__qmvU_">Technology</dt><dd class="GameSummary_gameTableRowContent__RW5fE">HTML5</dd><dt class="GameSummary_gameTableRowHeader__qmvU_">Platforms</dt><dd class="GameSummary_gameTableRowContent__RW5fE">Browser (desktop, mobile, tablet), CrazyGames App (iOS, Android), App Store (iOS, Android)</dd><dt class="GameSummary_gameTableRowHeader__qmvU_">Wiki pages</dt><dd class="GameSummary_gameTableRowContent__RW5fE"><div class="GameSummary_wikiLinks__xu_24"><a href="https://bloxd-io.fandom.com/wiki/Bloxd.io_Wiki" target="_blank">Fandom</a></div></dd></dl><div class="GameTags_gameTagChipContainer__F5xPO"><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/c/io"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">.io</p><span>119</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/meme-bloxy"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Meme & bloxy</p><span>24</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/sandbox"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Sandbox</p><span>36</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/mobile"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Mobile</p><span>1,881</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/parkour"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Parkour</p><span>50</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/minecraft"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Minecraft</p><span>77</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/jumping"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Jumping</p><span>148</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/third-person-shooter"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Third Person Shooter</p><span>76</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/build"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Building</p><span>176</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/with-friends"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">With Friends</p><span>127</span></div></a><a href="/multiplayer?tab=multiplayer&skipOverlay=1"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Multiplayer</p><span>332</span></div></a><a href="https://www.crazygames.com/t/block"><div class="TagGrid_tagPillContainer__rY0CY tagPill"><p class="">Block</p><span>93</span></div></a></div></div></div><div class="GameInfo_rightColumn__hExHC"><div class="" style="width:300px;display:block"><div style="text-align:center;width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;display:block;background:transparent"><div style="width:300px;height:250px;margin:auto;overflow:hidden;position:relative;background:rgba(71, 73, 103, 0.10);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px #28293D"><div class="MuiBox-root css-1dm7ec5" id="div-gpt-ad-1731941770755-0"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="GameInfo_roundedCornersContainer__D5D_p"><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY gameDescription_first" style="margin-block-end:1em"><p>Bloxd.io is an IO adventure game with Minecraft-style visuals and multiple game modes, including parkour challenges, creative sandbox building, and combat-based gameplay.</div><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY"><h2>How to Play Bloxd.io</h2><p>Bloxd.io is a sandbox game in which you navigate challenging obstacle courses by timing your jumps and movements accurately. In survival mode, you gather resources, craft tools, and fend off enemies to stay alive. There are several game modes to choose from to start the game, each with a variety of challenges.</p><h3>Bloxd.io Game Modes</h3><p>Choose from one of the many game modes to begin your Bloxd.io journey.</p><h4>BloxdHop.io</h4><p>In the BloxdHop game mode, your mission is to reach the end of the map within the given timeframe. To reach the end, you must hop through the level parkour-style onto blocks of various sizes.</p><h4>DoodleCube</h4><p>This game mode is similar to drawing games like Gartic.io. Players create objects based on the theme presented, and other users vote on how representative they are of that object.</p><h4>EvilTower</h4><p>The mission is to reach the top of the Evil Tower! Similar to BloxdHop, you use your parkour skills to reach the end. EvilTower is inspired by the Tower of Hell from a famous online platform.</p><h4>Peaceful</h4><p>Peaceful mode is like creative mode in Minecraft. You can roam freely, collecting resources and building here.</p><h4>CubeWarfare</h4><p>This game mode adds exciting battles. Compete against other players in a third-person shooter setting where you can also build blocks.</p><h4>Full list of game modes.</h4><p>Bloxd.io is regularly updated with fun new features and modes. Here is a selection of current game modes.</p><ul><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>BloxdHop.io</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>DoodleCube</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>EvilTower</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Peaceful</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>CubeWarfare</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Survival</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Peaceful</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Creative</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Bedwars</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Sky Wars</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>OneBlock</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Greenville</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Hide and Seek</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Murder Mystery</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Plots</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Pirates</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Survival Royale</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Worlds</li></ul><h3>More Games Like This</h3><p>Although Bloxd.io is a unique game that provides endless entertainment, there are similar titles to check out when you're finished playing. Other<a href="https://www.crazygames.com/c/io" target="_blank"> IO games</a> like this include <a href="https://www.crazygames.com/game/veck-io" target="_blank">Veck io</a> and <a href="https://www.crazygames.com/game/kour-io" target="_blank">Kour io</a>.</p><h3>Features</h3><ul><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Explore fun, voxelated worlds for free in your web browser.</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Play various game modes with different objectives.</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Earn gold from your achievements and spend it in the store.</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Join your friends in multiplayer games.</li></ul><h3>Release Date</h3><p>February 2021</p><h3>Developer</h3><p>Arthur made BloxdHop.io.</p><h3>Platform</h3><p>Web browser (desktop and mobile)</p></div><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY"><h3>Controls</h3><ul><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>WASD to move</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Shift or double-tap W to run</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>C, Z, \, or Caps Lock to crouch</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>T or Enter to chat</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>B to open shop</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>/ to start the command</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>O to open the menu</li></ul><h4>DoodleCube Controls</h4><ul><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Place blocks: right mouse button</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Destroy placed blocks: left mouse button</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>Switch blocks: number keys or the mouse middle button</li></ul><h4>Commands</h4><ul><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>/rtv - not a fan of this map? Vote to skip it!</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>/players - see the current players in your lobby</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>/xp - See your level and XP</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>/played - See how much time you've spent having tons of fun</li><li><span contenteditable="false"></span>/nobuffs - Play through the maps without any buffs to place on a separate leaderboard!</li></ul></div><h2 class="MuiBox-root css-14oh0q1">FAQ</h2><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY GameInfo_marginBlockEnd1__CZiMD"><div><h3>When did Bloxd.io come out?</h3><div><p>Bloxd.io came out in March 2021.</p></div></div><div><h3>Is Bloxd.io safe?</h3><div><p>As of 2024, there have been no reports of private information leaks. Create a personal account to ensure safe playing.</p></div></div><div><h3>What are the game modes in Bloxd.io?</h3><div><ul>
    <li>BloxdHop.io</li>
    <li>DoodleCube</li>
    <li>EvilTower</li>
    <li>Peaceful</li>
    <li>CubeWarfare</li>
    <li>Survival</li>
    <li>Peaceful</li>
    <li>Creative</li>
    <li>Bedwars</li>
    <li>Sky Wars</li>
    <li>OneBlock</li>
    <li>Greenville</li>
    <li>Hide and Seek</li>
    <li>Murder Mystery</li>
    <li>Plots</li>
    <li>Pirates</li>
    <li>Survival Royale</li>
    <li>Worlds</li>
</ul></div></div><div><h3>Who created Bloxd.io?</h3><div><p>An independent game developer called Arthur made this game!</p></div></div></div><div class="GameInfo_styledHtmlDiv__Zg2EY"><h2 style="margin-block-end:1em">Gameplay Video</h2><div style="width:440px;height:315px"></div></div></div><div class="GameInfo_roundedCornersContainer__D5D_p GameInfo_removeTopPadding__hI61b"><div class="GameInfo_gameInfoStoreButtonsContainer__snbxi"><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bloxd-io/id6720761703" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer nofollow noopener"><img src="https://imgs.crazygames.com/store-logos/apple-store.png?metadata=none&quality=60" alt="Apple Store Logo"/></a><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.bloxd.play" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer nofollow noopener"><img src="https://imgs.crazygames.com/store-logos/google-store-button.png?metadata=none&quality=60" alt="Google Play Logo"/></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="GamePageDesktop_rightSidebar__QgTMJ"><div class="GamePageDesktop_rightMpuContainer__tFXsw"><div class="" style="width:300px;display:block"><div style="text-align:center;width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;display:block;background:transparent"><div style="width:300px;height:250px;margin:auto;overflow:hidden;position:relative;background:rgba(71, 73, 103, 0.10);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px #28293D"><div class="MuiBox-root css-1dm7ec5" id="div-gpt-ad-1590672182999-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="GamePageDesktop_rightGridContainer__qJUvH"><div class="css-1w7kyz3" style="justify-content:center"><span class="MuiSkeleton-root MuiSkeleton-rectangular GameThumb_skeleton__f9HRh skeleton css-d7g3uh" style="width:calc(100% - 1px);height:calc(100% - 2px)"></span><span class="MuiSkeleton-root MuiSkeleton-rectangular GameThumb_skeleton__f9HRh skeleton css-d7g3uh" style="width:calc(100% - 1px);height:calc(100% - 2px)"></span><span class="MuiSkeleton-root MuiSkeleton-rectangular GameThumb_skeleton__f9HRh skeleton css-d7g3uh" 