dOnLeaderboards":"Get ranked on leaderboards","friends.upDrawer.privacyPreferences.confirmDisableLeaderboardWarning":"If you opt out, your highscores will be removed from all CrazyGames leaderboards and you wonât appear in rankings anymore. This wonât affect your game progress. ","friends.upDrawer.privacyPreferences.confirmDisableLeaderboardTitle":"Leave the Leaderboards","friends.upDrawer.privacyPreferences.confirmDisableLeaderboardWarningButton":"Yes, remove me","friends.upDrawer.friends.guestTitleSecondLine":"Stay connected.","friends.upDrawer.notifications.userInvitedToLeaderboard":[["user"]," challenges you in ",["game"]],"friends.popup.receiveGameInviteLeaderboard.accept":"Play","friends.updrawer.leaderboard.tooltip.challenge":"You can challenge this friend again tomorrow.","app.onboarding.auth.title":"Create your account","app.onboarding.auth.createPassword.title":"Create a password","app.onboarding.auth.username.title":"Pick a username","app.onboarding.end.cta":"Let's play","app.onboarding.end.subtitle":"We've sent you a verification email. If you don't see it, check your spam folder.","app.onboarding.end.title":"Your account is ready!","app.onboarding.notifications.subtitle":"Get friend invites and updates when your friends are playing.","app.onboarding.notifications.title":"Stay in the loop","app.onboarding.welcome.cta.guest":"Play as guest","app.onboarding.welcome.cta.login":"Log in / Sign up","app.onboarding.welcome.friends.subtitle":"Sign up to add friends and play together instantly","app.onboarding.welcome.friends.title":"Play with friends","app.onboarding.welcome.intro.subtitle":"Sign in to pick up where you left off on any device","app.onboarding.welcome.intro.title":"Never lose your progress","app.onboarding.welcome.notifications.subtitle":"Get invites and updates when friends are playing","app.onboarding.welcome.notifications.title":"Don't miss the fun","app.onboarding.start.title":"Welcome to","app.onboarding.start.title.line2":"CrazyGames","app.onboarding.start.description.ios":"Jump into 1,500+ games instantly","app.onboarding.start.description.android":"Jump into 2,500+ games instantly","app.forceUpdate.title":"Time to update","app.forceUpdate.subtitle":"A new version of CrazyGames is here. Update the app and keep the fun going.","app.forceUpdate.cta.updateNow":"Update"},"game":{"id":"18993","name":"Bloxd.io","slug":"bloxdhop-io","https":true,"rating":8.6,"upvotes":1111257,"downvotes":177174,"desktopUrl":"https://games.crazygames.com/en_US/bloxdhop-io/index.html","category":{"name":".io","slug":"io","enSlug":"io","thumbnail":"tags/io/thumb-1751538958512.png","gamesCount":119},"tags":[{"name":"Meme \u0026 bloxy","slug":"meme-bloxy","enSlug":"meme-bloxy","thumbnail":"tags/meme-bloxy/thumb-1773408611304.png","gamesCount":24},{"name":"Sandbox","slug":"sandbox","enSlug":"sandbox","thumbnail":"tags/sandbox/thumb-1751615740807.png","gamesCount":36},{"name":"Mobile","slug":"mobile","enSlug":"mobile","thumbnail":"tags/mobile/thumb-1714486209442.png","gamesCount":1881},{"name":"Parkour","slug":"parkour","enSlug":"parkour","thumbnail":"tags/parkour/thumb-1751604771630.png","gamesCount":50},{"name":"Minecraft","slug":"minecraft","enSlug":"minecraft","thumbnail":"tags/minecraft/thumb-1751616400159.png","gamesCount":77},{"name":"Jumping","slug":"jumping","enSlug":"jumping","thumbnail":"tags/jumping/thumb-1750933989031.png","gamesCount":148},{"name":"Third Person Shooter","slug":"third-person-shooter","enSlug":"third-person-shooter","thumbnail":"tags/third-person-shooter/thumb-1751453962301.png","gamesCount":76},{"name":"Building","slug":"build","enSlug":"build","thumbnail":"tags/build/thumb-1751474803520.png","gamesCount":176},{"name":"With Friends","slug":"with-friends","enSlug":"with-friends","thumbnail":"tags/with-friends/thumb-1751479863974.png","gamesCount":127},{"name":"Multiplayer","slug":"multiplayer","enSlug":"multiplayer","thumbnail":"tags/multiplayer/thumb-1751540045563.png","gamesCount":332},{"name":"Block","slug":"block","enSlug":"block","thumbnail":"tags/block/thumb-1750933444988.png","gamesCount":93}],"pageTitle":"Bloxd io ð² Play on CrazyGames","descriptionFirst":"\u003cp\u003eBloxd.io is an IO adventure game with Minecraft-style visuals and multiple game modes, including parkour challenges, creative sandbox building, and combat-based gameplay.","descriptionRest":"\u003ch2\u003eHow to Play Bloxd.io\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eBloxd.io is a sandbox game in which you navigate challenging obstacle courses by timing your jumps and movements accurately. In survival mode, you gather resources, craft tools, and fend off enemies to stay alive. There are several game modes to choose from to start the game, each with a variety of challenges.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eBloxd.io Game Modes\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eChoose from one of the many game modes to begin your Bloxd.io journey.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eBloxdHop.io\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn the BloxdHop game mode, your mission is to reach the end of the map within the given timeframe. To reach the end, you must hop through the level parkour-style onto blocks of various sizes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eDoodleCube\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis game mode is similar to drawing games like Gartic.io. Players create objects based on the theme presented, and other users vote on how representative they are of that object.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eEvilTower\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe mission is to reach the top of the Evil Tower! Similar to BloxdHop, you use your parkour skills to reach the end. EvilTower is inspired by the Tower of Hell from a famous online platform.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003ePeaceful\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003ePeaceful mode is like creative mode in Minecraft. You can roam freely, collecting resources and building here.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eCubeWarfare\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis game mode adds exciting battles. Compete against other players in a third-person shooter setting where you can also build blocks.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eFull list of game modes.\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eBloxd.io is regularly updated with fun new features and modes. Here is a selection of current game modes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eBloxdHop.io\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eDoodleCube\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eEvilTower\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ePeaceful\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eCubeWarfare\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eSurvival\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ePeaceful\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eCreative\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eBedwars\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eSky Wars\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eOneBlock\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eGreenville\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eHide and Seek\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eMurder Mystery\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ePlots\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ePirates\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eSurvival Royale\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eWorlds\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003eMore Games Like This\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlthough Bloxd.io is a unique game that provides endless entertainment, there are similar titles to check out when you're finished playing. Other\u003ca href=\"https://www.crazygames.com/c/io\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e IO games\u003c/a\u003e like this include \u003ca href=\"https://www.crazygames.com/game/veck-io\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eVeck io\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.crazygames.com/game/kour-io\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eKour io\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eFeatures\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eExplore fun, voxelated worlds for free in your web browser.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ePlay various game modes with different objectives.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eEarn gold from your achievements and spend it in the store.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eJoin your friends in multiplayer games.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003eRelease Date\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eFebruary 2021\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eDeveloper\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eArthur made BloxdHop.io.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003ePlatform\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eWeb browser (desktop and mobile)\u003c/p\u003e","metaDescription":"Bloxd.io is an IO adventure game with Minecraft-style visuals and multiple game modes, including parkour challenges, creative sandbox building, and combat-based gameplay.","developer":"Arthur","developerId":"Jk6RmECLXwajwbVlm7hzB4O56ZL2","controls":"\u003ch3\u003eControls\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eWASD to move\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eShift or double-tap W to run\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eC, Z, \\, or Caps Lock to crouch\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eT or Enter to chat\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eB to open shop\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e/ to start the command\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eO to open the menu\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eDoodleCube Controls\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ePlace blocks: right mouse button\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eDestroy placed blocks: left mouse button\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003eSwitch blocks: number keys or the mouse middle button\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eCommands\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e/rtv - not a fan of this map? Vote to skip it!\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e/players - see the current players in your lobby\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e/xp - See your level and XP\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e/played - See how much time you've spent having tons of fun\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan contenteditable=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e/nobuffs - Play through the maps without any buffs to place on a separate leaderboard!\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e","customStructuredData":"[{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"VideoObject\",\"name\":\"Playing Bloxd.Io Evil Tower\",\"description\":\"Make SURE to Like, Comment, Subscribe! And Watch till the end to find out if I beated the Tower or I died.\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/v7Hv437JNUM/default.jpg\",\"uploadDate\":\"2021-09-07T04:30:07Z\",\"duration\":\"PT4M6S\",\"embedUrl\":\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/v7Hv437JNUM\"},{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"When did Bloxd.io come out?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"\u003cp\u003eBloxd.io came out in March 2021.\u003c/p\u003e\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is Bloxd.io safe?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"\u003cp\u003eAs of 2024, there have been no reports of private information leaks. Create a personal account to ensure safe playing.\u003c/p\u003e\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the game modes in Bloxd.io?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"\u003cul\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eBloxdHop.io\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eDoodleCube\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eEvilTower\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003ePeaceful\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eCubeWarfare\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eSurvival\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003ePeaceful\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eCreative\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eBedwars\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eSky Wars\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eOneBlock\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eGreenville\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eHide and Seek\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eMurder Mystery\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003ePlots\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003ePirates\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eSurvival Royale\u003c/li\u003e\\n    \u003cli\u003eWorlds\u003c/li\u003e\\n\u003c/ul\u003e\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Who created Bloxd.io?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"\u003cp\u003eAn independent game developer called Arthur made this game!\u003c/p\u003e\"}}]}]","playStoreUrl":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.bloxd.play","a